9790,"uid":7278,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T11:58:42.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.rthk.hk/tv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rthk.hk%2Ftv&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BSiEyVFbloTKGHdwbQdNTMZo%3D&h=83e1d11c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.rthk.hk/tv</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:02:27.000Z","msg":"pin plz"},{"pid":"8ca27e1c451d81784ecb184f9fe4457a0e851817","tid":2029790,"uid":304769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:02:40.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">借個位：黑色五毛風向警告，大量五毛正在吹襲連登</span></strong><br />\n正視聽，<span style=\"color: red;\">國安法唔係攬炒，美國做野先係</span><br />\n<br />\n大家<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比五毛帶風向去支持國安法，否則會比對家spin成香港人支持國安法</span>。只有<span style=\"color: red;\">香港人強烈反對下強行通過，美國才有做野的理由</span>。大家小心。<br />\n<br />\n借個位<br />\n連登一向錯曬風向，<span style=\"color: red;\">英國點日落都好，香港問題上都係重要持分者</span>，必須engage。<br />\n我地唔係要拉攏政府班奶共狗（例如Dominic Rabb），而係要<span style=\"color: red;\">拉攏英國民意</span>啊。英國係民主國家，民意最重要。英國民意決定stand with Hong Kong/Boycott China，BJ以至成個政府都無得唔跟。<span style=\"color: red;\">宜家武肺英國死左就快十萬人，正是推動報仇民意好機會</span>。<br />\n<br />\n另外要借助美國向英國施壓，因為<span style=\"color: red;\">美國有動機（報武肺之仇）同拳頭，加英國有理由（聯合聲明），兩個加埋先容易嚮香港問題做野</span>"},{"pid":"8ec56a930f5ee4dd3d6c68251a4d30a65a42fbe4","tid":2029790,"uid":119408,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:03:01.000Z","msg":"不如集中推呢個?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/2028763/\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/2028763/</a>"},{"pid":"58fd902d63b9fe2e625fbf850413883d19601d9d","tid":2029790,"uid":7278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T12:03:10.000Z","msg":"用rthk screen app 睇都得㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c75b11da8c02d9912af4e4465ced1fb2e2d8